                    android:text="National Income concepts - GNP – GDP – NNP– Per Capita Income – Measurement of National Income-Output method- Income method and Expenditure method -Sectoral Contribution to GDP– Money-Static and Dynamic Functions of Money-Inflation – causes of inflation – measures to control inflation – Demand Pull inflation – cost push inflation – Effects of Inflation – Deflation."
